lead_paragraph: New Zealand's cricket team will leave for their tour of Africa as scheduled next Monday despite unrest in Zimbabwe, though they will monitor the situation before deciding whether to continue into the country for two tests, a spokesman said on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: No Changes to Africa Tour Plans but NZ Monitoring Zimbabwe
headline.main: No Changes to Africa Tour Plans but NZ Monitoring Zimbabwe
